<br>
We will assemble at the East End of Nexus at 2PM sharp, chat channel &quot;bardguts&quot;, PoP NOT required (but we will use raid tool if all attending have PoP)<br>
<br>
We need at least 2 full groups approximately levels 45 and up.  Please sign up with LEVEL, CLASS, and whether you have POP here <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
We need to kill kill kill because there are many placeholders.  Expect the camp to take a minimum of three hours and possibly as much as six hours. XP and loot are decent through the mid 50s.<br>
<br>
Baronius, senior bard of KotC, will receive the first set of guts, and should we be so lucky to get a second set, they will go to Gingerbay of the KotC.  All other loot will be randomed or distributed on Need-before-Greed basis.   <p>Madrib; <br>
